@WheaterRhys @PhillipsPOBrien @KpsZSU Most western pilots aren’t actively fighting a hot war during training; watching their nation burn.

(Perhaps not a match for NATO AF/Naval aviators after two weeks, but they only have to be good enough to stay in the sky and deter the Russians.)

Necessity is a wonderful teacher

